snippet.title: Doki-Doki Universe Story Trailer
snippet.description:
Take on the role of an abandoned little robot named Model QT377665.  To avoid being scrapped by the factory that made you, you must travel the universe and learn what it means to be human by helping characters along the way. 

For more info visit: http://us.playstation.com/ps4/games/doki-doki-universe-ps4.html
